<div class="flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100 py-6">
  <div class="max-w-4xl w-full mx-auto px-6">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">About End</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Learn more about our application and what we do</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content Cards -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Mission Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="bg-indigo-100 rounded-full p-3 mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Our Mission</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          End is designed to help you manage your tasks efficiently and bring closure to your daily responsibilities. 
          We believe in providing a simple, intuitive interface that helps you focus on what matters most.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="bg-emerald-100 rounded-full p-3 mr-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">Key Features</h2>
        </div>
        <ul class="text-slate-600 space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Drag and drop todo ordering</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Due date tracking with notifications</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Responsive design for all devices</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">Built for Simplicity</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          End was created with a focus on providing a clean, distraction-free environment for task management. 
          We understand that productivity tools should enhance your workflow, not complicate it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Our application combines modern web technologies with thoughtful design to deliver an experience that 
          feels both powerful and approachable. Whether you're managing personal projects or team tasks, 
          End adapts to your needs.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We're constantly improving End based on user feedback and emerging best practices in task management. 
          Your productivity journey is our priority.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Navigation -->
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6">
        <%= link_to "Back to Todos", todos_path, 
              class: "text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 font-medium transition-colors" %>
        <%= link_to "Contact Us", contact_path, 
              class: "text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-700 font-medium transition-colors" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
